How do I add ad credit to my account?

To add ad credit to your account, follow these steps:
1. Log in to your NewsBreak account.
2. Navigate to the 'Billing' section.
3. Look for the option to redeem an ad credit.
4. Enter the code for your ad credit and confirm.
If you need more detailed instructions, you can refer to this article: [How to redeem a NewsBreak ad credit](https://help.newsbreak.com/hc/en-us/articles/17959734533005-NewsBreak-Advertising-Cost). Let me know if you have any other questions!
